excel.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch5\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/ways-maximize-productivity-in-excel/\" title=\"9 ways to maximize your productivity in Excel\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e 9 ways to maximize your productivity in Excel \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/h5\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith the right strategy, you can make Excel an even more powerful tool for productivity\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"excel-can-make-a-great-to-do-list\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4 \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Excel can make a great to-do list \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"manage-your-daily-tasks\"\u003e Manage your daily tasks \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2082\" height=\"1392\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Task templates in Excel\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel-1.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e With Excel, you can build your own \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/how-i-built-a-to-do-list-in-excel-that-actually-works/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eto-do-list with ease\u003c/a\u003e. There are a ton of task management apps out there, and they can make it harder to keep up with deadlines and priorities in some instances. Excel is pretty straightforward and easy to follow, which is why it makes sense to build a to-do list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you want to make your own Excel to-do-list, it\u0026#39;s pretty easy but a bit time-consuming, though there are \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/best-project-management-and-planner-templates-for-microsoft-excel/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea lot of Excel templates\u003c/a\u003e that you can choose from to make it easier if you need to do build a to-do-list but want to do it without putting in the time investment to building your own.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"make-a-back-to-school-planner\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Make a back to school planner \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"great-for-students\"\u003e Great for students \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2158\" height=\"1692\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"best-project-management-and planner-Excel-templates-8\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/best-project-management-and-planner-excel-templates-8.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e If you\u0026#39;re on your way back to college or school, then a back to school planner in Excel is a great way to help you get together exactly what you need and automate the process as much as you can. There are countless templates out there with pre-filled options for you, but the idea is that you can create a list of things that you need and check them off as you go.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you\u0026#39;re on your way back to education and looking for a way to keep on top of what you need to bring with you, then a back to school planner in Excel is a great way to do just that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"track-your-finances-and-calculate-a-daily-spending-budget\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2 \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Track your finances and calculate a daily spending budget \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"make-it-easier-to-reign-in-your-spending\"\u003e Make it easier to reign in your spending \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"2387\" height=\"1406\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Personal monthly budget template\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/08/finance-and-budget-templates-11.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eExcel can also be an excellent tool for \u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/10-free-budget-and-finance-templates-for-excel/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003etracking your finances\u003c/a\u003e and setting a daily or monthly spending budget. With a simple spreadsheet, you can categorize your expenses, input your income, and monitor your spending habits in real time. This can help you identify where you\u0026#39;re overspending and make adjustments accordingly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThere are numerous pre-made templates available that can help you track bills, debts, savings goals, and everyday expenses. By automating calculations, Excel can instantly show you how much you have left in your budget after each expense. This is especially helpful for those trying to save money or stick to a financial plan.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"health-planner\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e Health planner \u003c/span\u003e \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"track-your-health-metrics\"\u003e Track your health metrics \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source: Microsoft\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1034\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fitness-vision-modern-simple-2-1.png\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eSource: Microsoft\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eExcel is a fantastic tool for keeping a detailed record of your health data. You can set up a health tracker to log important health metrics such as your weight, blood pressure, heart rate, glucose levels, and calorie intake over time. You can then have a comprehensive overview of your health progress and can spot any patterns or changes in your well-being. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOn top of that, you can use formulas to calculate averages, track changes, and even set goals for weight loss, fitness improvement, or diet adjustments. You can create graphs and charts that show trends over time, giving you a visual representation of your progress. For example, you could see how your blood pressure has changed over the last few months or monitor fluctuations in your weight on a weekly basis.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"17a9-4ada-b3b5394681c0\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/how-i-built-a-to-do-list-in-excel-that-actually-works/\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"how to create a to-do list in Excel\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/create-to-do-list-in-excel.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch5\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/how-i-built-a-to-do-list-in-excel-that-actually-works/\" title=\"How I built a to-do list in Excel that actually works\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e How I built a to-do list in Excel that actually works \u003c/a\u003e \u003c/h5\u003e\u003cp\u003eCreate a functional task list in Excel for getting things done\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
